<div class="relative isolate overflow-hidden">
  <%= render 'top_links' %>
  <div class="absolute left-[calc(50%-4rem)] top-10 -z-10 transform-gpu blur-3xl sm:left-[calc(50%-18rem)] lg:left-48 lg:top-[calc(50%-30rem)] xl:left-[calc(50%-24rem)]" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="aspect-1108/632 w-[69.25rem] bg-linear-to-r from-[#80caff] to-[#4f46e5] opacity-20" style="clip-path: polygon(73.6% 51.7%, 91.7% 11.8%, 100% 46.4%, 97.4% 82.2%, 92.5% 84.9%, 75.7% 64%, 55.3% 47.5%, 46.5% 49.4%, 45% 62.9%, 50.3% 87.2%, 21.3% 64.1%, 0.1% 100%, 5.4% 51.1%, 21.4% 63.9%, 58.9% 0.2%, 73.6% 51.7%)"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-16 pt-8 sm:pb-16 lg:px-8 lg:pt-40 flex flex-col">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-x-6 ml-8 mb-8">
      <%= landing_pages_h1 title: "#{current_theme_display_name} Data Retention Policy" %>
    </div>
    <div class="text-white <%= document_bg_class_for_current_theme %> rounded-lg p-8 w-full">
      <p class="my-4 text-gray-300">
        We are committed to safeguarding user data while balancing operational requirements and compliance with applicable laws. 
        This policy outlines how data is retained, accessed, and managed.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3x1 font-bold leading-10">1. Read-Only Data Access for Expired Accounts</h2>
      <p class="my-4 text-gray-300">
        Users may be granted limited, read-only access to their data under certain circumstances, typically in the advent of 
        expired user workspaces. This access is provided to allow users to retrieve or review their data. During this time, 
        no changes, updates, or additions to the data will be permitted.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3x1 font-bold leading-10">2. Data Deletion or Anonymisation</h2>
      <p class="my-4 text-gray-300">
        We reserve the right to permanently delete or anonymise user data in accordance with our data retention practices 
        and applicable legal requirements. Data deletion or anonymisation ensures compliance with privacy laws and protects 
        user confidentiality.
      </p>
      <p class="my-4 text-gray-300">
        Whenever possible, we will notify users of any impending data deletion or anonymisation activities. Users may also
        request the deletion of their data by contacting us via the
        <%= landing_pages_link_to 'Privacy Contact Form', privacy_contacts_path %>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3x1 font-bold leading-10">3. Compliance with Legal Regulations</h2>
      <p class="my-4 text-gray-300">
        We comply with relevant data privacy regulations, including but not limited to those covered by Australian Federal 
        and South Australian privacy legislation. Our data handling practices aim to meet the highest standards of 
        integrity and user rights.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3x1 font-bold leading-10">4. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="my-4 text-gray-300">
        We reserve the right to update or modify this Data Retention Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on 
        this page, and your continued use of the platform after such changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3x1 font-bold leading-10">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="my-4 text-gray-300">
        If you have any questions or concerns about this Data Retention Policy, please contact us via the 
        <%= landing_pages_link_to 'Privacy Contact Form', privacy_contacts_path %>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
